Invocation Name: box fan sounds
des: The constant hum of a working box fan helps so many people fall asleeo every night! Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Box Fan Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
